-- China Housing Official Says May Loosen Third-Home Loan Policy, Daily Says
-- Bloomberg News
-- 2010-07-12T01:47:11Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2010-07-12/china-housing-official-says-may-loosen-third-home-loan-policy-daily-says.html

          
          
             China may loosen limitations on
third-home loans as the curbs reaped their intended effects on
real estate market, the Southern Metropolis Daily reported,
citing Qin Hong, a researcher from Ministry of Housing and
Urban-Rural Development.  
